<para>This creates a blank screen and exits either when you close the window or when you press ESCAPE: <programlisting><codeline><highlight class="preprocessor">#include<sp/>&quot;<ref refid="softrender_8hpp" kindref="compound">softrender.hpp</ref>&quot;</highlight><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"></highlight><highlight class="keywordtype">int</highlight><highlight class="normal"><sp/>main()</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">{</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><ref refid="classsoftrender_1_1window__t" kindref="compound">softrender::window_t</ref><sp/>window{<sp/>1280,<sp/>720<sp/>};</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/></highlight><highlight class="keywordflow">while</highlight><highlight class="normal">(!window.closed())<sp/>{</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>window.<ref refid="classsoftrender_1_1window__t_1ac497299341c58212a213bb9c42d673d8" kindref="member">draw</ref>();</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>}</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">}</highlight></codeline>
</programlisting></para><para>To draw a red point in the middle of the screen: <programlisting><codeline><highlight class="preprocessor">#include<sp/>&quot;<ref refid="softrender_8hpp" kindref="compound">softrender.hpp</ref>&quot;</highlight><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
